'''克雷格·約翰·康塞爾'''（{{lang-en|'''Craig John Counsell'''}}，{{bd|1970年|8月21日||}}），[[美國職業棒球大聯盟|大聯盟]]選手，現已退役。自2015年起，他於[[密爾瓦基釀酒人|密爾瓦基釀酒人]]擔任總教練一職。

康塞爾在季後賽的演出令人印象深刻，尤以2001年國聯冠軍系列賽為最，該年他獲得系列賽最有價值球員（MVP）的肯定。此外，他舉棒過頭的打擊準備姿勢亦相當具有記憶點。

== 生平 ==
=== 早年 ===
康塞爾出生於[[印第安纳州|印第安纳州]][[南本德_(印第安纳州)|南本德]]，在[[威斯康辛州|威斯康辛州]]{{link-en|白魚灣 (威斯康辛州)|Whitefish Bay, Wisconsin|白魚灣}}成長，高中時期開始接觸棒球活動。他的父親約翰·康塞爾（John Counsell）服務於釀酒人球團，擔任發言和公關部門的負責人。大學時期，康塞爾就讀於[[聖母大學|聖母大學]]，持續棒球運動<ref name=grewup>{{cite web|url=http://www.jsonline.com/blogs/sports/302412841.html|title=Craig Counsell grew up with the Brewers|author=Tom Haudricourt|work=jsonline.com|access-date=May 4, 2015|archive-date=2016-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160614120258/http://www.jsonline.com/blogs/sports/302412841.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://fox6now.com/2016/03/23/craig-counsell-in-his-first-full-year-as-brewers-manager-running-his-very-first-spring-training/|title=Craig Counsell in his first full year as Brewers manager, running his very first spring training|date=2016-03-24|access-date=2016-06-20|archive-date=2016-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160819172504/http://fox6now.com/2016/03/23/craig-counsell-in-his-first-full-year-as-brewers-manager-running-his-very-first-spring-training/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在大學校隊，他留下打擊率.306、得分204分、打點166的成績。1992年，康塞爾自聖母大學畢業<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://und.com/irish-alum-craig-counsell-retires-after-16-years-in-mlb/|title=Irish Alum Craig Counsell Retires After 16 Years In MLB|date=2012-01-17|website=Notre Dame Fighting Irish - Official Athletics Website|language=en-US|access-date=2019-10-02|archive-date=2021-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210306013750/https://und.com/irish-alum-craig-counsell-retires-after-16-years-in-mlb/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 選手生涯 ===
[[科羅拉多落磯|科羅拉多落磯]]在1992年選秀第11輪選中了康塞爾，他於1995年9月17日首次登上大聯盟賽場，當季他僅短暫為洛磯出賽三場，之後未再回到大聯盟。1997年7月，康塞爾被交易至國聯新銳隊伍[[佛羅里達馬林魚|佛羅里達馬林魚]]，立刻站穩二壘先發位置。[[1997年世界大賽|1997年世界大賽]]第7戰，康塞爾在第9局以犧牲打幫助球隊追平比數，而後在第11局替球隊跑回致勝一分，康塞爾也獲得個人第一枚冠軍戒指<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/FLO/FLO199710260.shtml|title=October 26, 1997 World Series Game 7, Indians at Marlins - Baseball-Reference.com|work=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2015-05-04|archive-date=2019-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190815202746/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/FLO/FLO199710260.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1999年6月，康塞爾被交易至[[洛杉磯道奇|洛杉磯道奇]]，但在翌年春訓時遭到釋出，康塞爾轉而與[[亞利桑那響尾蛇|亞利桑那響尾蛇]]簽約。{{link-en|2001年國家聯盟冠軍系列賽|2001 National League Championship Series}}，他有21打數8安打的表現，榮膺系列賽最有價值球員<ref>{{cite web|url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/sports/baseball/diamondbacks/2001-10-22-counsell-mvp.htm|title=USATODAY.com - MVP Counsell looks like a kid, plays like a man|work=usatoday.com|access-date=2015-05-04|archive-date=2015-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150504193838/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/sports/baseball/diamondbacks/2001-10-22-counsell-mvp.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在當年的[[2001年世界大賽|世界大賽]]第7戰，康塞爾遭[[马里安诺·李维拉|马里安诺·李维拉]]的觸身球擊中，他走向一壘壘包，從而目送{{link-en|路易·岡薩雷茲 (外野手)|Luis Gonzalez (outfielder, born 1967)|路易·岡薩雷茲}}打下冠軍的致勝一擊<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/ARI/ARI200111040.shtml|title=November 4, 2001 World Series Game 7, Yankees at Diamondbacks - Baseball-Reference.com|work=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=May 4, 2015|archive-date=2017-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171116133846/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/ARI/ARI200111040.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2003年季後，康塞爾被交易至[[密爾瓦基釀酒人|密爾瓦基釀酒人]]{{NoteTag|與康塞爾一同被交易的，還有{{tsl|en|Chris Capuano|克里斯·卡普安諾}}、{{tsl|en|Chad Moeller|查德·莫勒}}、{{tsl|en|Lyle Overbay|萊爾·歐佛貝}}、{{tsl|en|Jorge de la Rosa|荷黑·德·拉·羅薩}}與[[朱尼爾·斯皮維|朱尼爾·斯皮維]]等人。}}。釀酒人時期的康塞爾主要擔任游擊守備。2004年季後，他再次重返亞利桑那<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/c/counscr01.shtml|title=Craig Counsell Statistics and History - Baseball-Reference.com|work=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2015-05-04|archive-date=2021-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210618130335/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/c/counscr01.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
[[File:Craig_Counsell_(929748198).jpg|right]]

2007年球季，康塞爾再一次離開亞利桑那，並選擇與釀酒人再續前緣，並轉型成為內野工具人角色。2008年8月16日，達成生涯千安{{NoteTag|對手為道奇投手[[德瑞克·洛夫|德瑞克·洛夫]]。}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hardballtimes.com/tht-live/craig-counsell-career-highlights/|title=Craig Counsell career highlights|access-date=2016-06-20|archive-date=2016-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160815162000/http://www.hardballtimes.com/tht-live/craig-counsell-career-highlights/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。到了2011年球季，康塞爾是國聯第4年長的資深球員（40歲），卻有一項傲人的紀錄：在現役球員中，其.991守備率是二壘位置次高者<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/NL/2011-other-leaders.shtml |title=2011 National League Awards, All-Stars, & More Leaders |publisher=Baseball-Reference.com |access-date=2011-10-03 |archive-date=2021-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421230004/http://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/NL/2011-other-leaders.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leaders/fielding_perc_2b_active.shtml |title=Active Leaders & Records for Fielding % as 2B |publisher=Baseball-Reference.com |access-date=2011-10-03 |archive-date=2019-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190425024331/https://www.baseball-reference.com/leaders/fielding_perc_2b_active.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2012年季前，康塞爾宣布卸下球員身分，加入釀酒人球團運作。

=== 執教 ===
退役後的康塞爾，自釀酒人總教練{{tsl|en|Doug Melvin}}{{譯名請求}}的特別助理起步<ref>{{cite web|url=http://espn.go.com/mlb/story/_/id/7470907/craig-counsell-retires-join-milwaukee-brewers-front-office|title=Craig Counsell retires, will join Milwaukee Brewers' front office|work=ESPN.com|access-date=2015-05-04|date=2012-01-17|archive-date=2016-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307031118/http://espn.go.com/mlb/story/_/id/7470907/craig-counsell-retires-join-milwaukee-brewers-front-office|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年球季，他曾在釀酒人主場擔任球賽講評工作<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.jsonline.com/blogs/sports/248266401.html|title=Craig Counsell and Darryl Hamilton will call Brewers radio games Uecker elects to miss|last=Wolfley|first=Bob|publisher=jsonline.com|date=2014-03-03|access-date=2021-04-07|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304033207/http://www.jsonline.com/blogs/sports/248266401.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年5月3日，時任釀酒人總教練[[羅恩·羅尼克|羅恩·羅尼克]]遭開除，康塞爾於翌日受命為新任總教練，與球團達成了三年合約的協議<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.jsonline.com/blogs/sports/302412841.html |title=Brewers give Craig Counsell three-year deal as manager |author=Tom Haudricourt |date=2015-05-04 |publisher=Milwaukee, Wisconsin Journal Sentinel |work=www.jsonline.com |access-date=2015-05-04 |archive-date=2016-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160614120258/http://www.jsonline.com/blogs/sports/302412841.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

康塞爾接任時，釀酒人仍在重建階段，前兩年戰績僅有61勝、73勝<ref name="managerial record">{{cite web|title=Craig Counsell|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/managers/counscr01.shtml|website=Baseball Reference|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|access-date=2016-08-02|archive-date=2021-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210418012040/https://www.baseball-reference.com/managers/counscr01.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年的釀酒人打出驚奇之旅，戰績（86勝）爬升至國聯中區第2位，惜未晉級。該年康塞爾在國聯最佳教練票選中列名第4。

